replies.body:
Please don't necro threads.  It's pretty clear that this thread was created before Sylas was even heard of by the community so bumping it now isn't really helpful and can only confuse others.  I'm going to lock this thread up as a result.

Let's make a new thread if we want to discuss Sylas' motives and "evil" Demacians.

{{sticker:poppy-wink}}
